node.text: From reefs to ridges, explore the beauty of the Philippines through the eyes of the locals. While 2020 has been a year of change for travel, the Philippines is excited to invite local visitors to explore the beautiful islands. The #BDTeam had the pleasure of working with @tourism_phl to highlight beautiful places around the Philippines. The opportunities for exploration are endless-from the Hundred Island National Park in Pangasinan to exploring the Suba and Culili Sand Dunes in Ilocos Norte.

node.text:
With an incredibly rich history, being an “Egyptian” can have many facets especially when it comes to creativity. Today, we’re sharing a unique story dedicated to any creative who intends to carve their own path no matter the circumstances. 

“It’s proof that the end product most of the time doesn’t pan out the way you expect it. And its by having expectations that you hinder your potential.” - @matiasderada

Watch this beautiful film on Beautiful Destinations Youtube channel. 🇪🇬

🎥 @matiasderada #BDTeam

Bristol Bay, one of Alaska’s most treasured natural wonders, is under threat. @world_wildlife 

It’s home to an irreplaceable ecosystem and one of the last salmon strongholds. Not only that, its iconic wildlife has sprung up a sustainable tourism industry which effects thousands of Alaskan livelihoods.

All of this is under threat if the Pebble Mine moves forward. The recent approval of the environmental impact statement has made it clear that our voices need to be heard. 

Nature and people can’t live without fresh water, and Bristol Bay is the lifeblood that sustains every species calling the region home. 

On a recent trip to Alaska, the #BDTeam and WWF Ambassador, @jeremyjauncey, learned firsthand about the conservation community’s fight against Pebble Mine.

node.text: As New York City starts to open back up, we wanted to take a moment to reflect on the efforts of heroes in the hospitality industry who have been helping our frontline workers. @fsnewyork was the first hotel in New York City to open its door to our frontline workers and provide them with a safe haven to stay during such an uncertain time. They quickly transformed the hotel into a near medical-grade facility. Over 300 medical workers called @fsnewyork home during this time as they were provided rooms free of charge. This allowed them to keep their own families safe as they focused on their work and taking care of patients. ❤️ (🎥: @loganlambert 📸: @loganstrongarms 📍: Four Seasons Hotel New York)

node.text:
These snippets of Amalfi Coast via @lumadeline have got us daydreaming about endless summer days in this Italian paradise. ☀️

Brimming with breezy corners, quaint nooks, and ocean views for days, the famous Amalfi Coast lives up to its reputation for being one of the dreamiest getaways. With a cool drink in hand and the delightful flavors of fresh local cuisine, spending a vacation here will truly make your heart, tummy, and soul full. 🇮🇹

If you're in dire need of a vacation, let this be your sign to go for it and book that well-deserved trip! Where's your next idyllic getaway? 🍋

📽 @lumadeline
📍 Amalfi Coast, Italy
🎶 Matteo Rossanese - Sunny Day

Taking a dip with @samanthalreid via @wilderness_addict. 💦 Alberta flourishes with refreshing lakes and soaring mountains. Unlike lakes in other parts of Canada, the mountain lakes of Alberta are quite special as they're usually set against a superb panorama of snowcapped peaks. Needless to say, these glacier-fed mountain lakes are invigoratingly cold! 🇨🇦

Would you rather swim in tropical waters or chilly glacial lakes? 🏊‍♀️

📽 @wilderness_addict 
🙎‍♀️ @samanthalreid 
📍 Canadian Rockies, Alberta, Canada
🎶 Olivia Rodrigo - deja vu

Dreaming of @@soufian_outman's sunny Moroccan getaway at Playa Cara Blanca. Have you heard of this beach in Morocco? 🇲🇦

If you're looking for a quick beach trip in Morocco, make your way to the pristine paradise of Playa Cara Blanca. With turquoise water and golden sand, it's a coastal getaway that's free for all—having no amenities and only nature to enjoy. Whether you're a solo traveler or with a travel crew, you'll surely have a relaxing time at this refreshing hideaway. 💙

📽 @soufian_outman 
📍 Playa Cara Blanca, Morocco
🎶 Drenchill Feat. Indiiana - Never Never

A change of altitude via @hilling89. 😌 When was the last time a moment took your breath away during your travels? ☁️

Norway’s Lofoten Islands offer the most dramatic and rewarding landscapes, which can range from endless ocean views to a remarkable sea of clouds. Any nature lover and adventure seeker will have a field day in this archipelago brimming with pristine natural scenery. 🇳🇴

If you're feeling stuck in a rut, take this as a sign to spend time in nature with your loved ones—it can do wonders! Tag your travel buddy and a dog-loving friend, too. 🐶

📽 @hilling89
📍 Lofoten, Norway

Celebrating BD's milestone of reaching 20 million followers on Instagram! 🎉 We're commemorating this special moment with you via @waketowaketc's amazing video of @austinkeen and @jojothedolphin making waves in the Turks and Caicos Islands. 🌊

The BD team has always taken pride in positive storytelling and spotlighting great talents at @beautifuldestinations, @beautifulhotels, @beautifulcuisines, and @beautifulmatters. We hope we have inspired you all to travel, connect, and leave a positive impact on the world. 🌎 Despite our differences, our love for travel unites us and we are so honored to be sharing this incredible bond with each one of you. 🙏🏼

To all our followers: THANK YOU for being part of our journey and for being the reason why we do what we do. Here's to cherishing more beautiful moments in life—together and onwards! ✈️

When did you start following our account? Take us down memory lane and share how you discovered us!

📽 @waketowaketc

A leap of faith with @escolhas_de_simone over the Cachoeira da Fumaça, one of the most impressive waterfalls in Brazil. 💦

The waterfall has a height of about 45 meters and is one of the most sought-after attractions in the municipality of Nova Ponte. Once you get to the top, you'll be greeted by an incredible vantage point that offers lush views of the surrounding forest. 🇧🇷

Would you dare try this rope jump? 😳🔥

📽 @escolhas_de_simone
📍 Cachoeira da Fumaça, Brazil
🎶 Trampoline (Jauz Remix) - SHAED
